Terms and Conditions of Use

1. Introduction

These Terms of Use (the "Terms") regulate your use of STOQ (the "App"). By using the App, you agree to these Terms. If you do not agree, you should not use the App.

2. Usage Rights

The App is provided under a personal, non-exclusive, non-transferable license. You may not copy, modify, distribute, or use the App for illegal purposes.

3. Registration and Account

You must provide accurate details during registration and are responsible for all actions performed under your account.

4. Payments and Subscriptions

Paid services must be settled as specified. Subscriptions renew automatically unless canceled before expiry.

5. Responsibility

The App is provided "as is". We are not liable for loss or damage resulting from its use or downtime.

6. Changes and Updates

We may update these Terms or the App anytime. Continuing use means you accept the new Terms.

7. Discontinuation of Use

Access may be suspended for violations. You can also stop using the App anytime by deleting your account.

8. Applicable Law

These Terms follow the laws of your country/region. Disputes will be handled by the competent courts.

9. Contact Us

For any questions, reach out at{" "} contact@stoq.ai .

{/* Privacy Policy Section */}

Privacy Policy

Introduction

This Privacy Policy describes how we collect, use, store, and protect your personal information when using STOQ.

1. What Data We Collect

We may collect personal data (name, email, phone), account details, warehouse data, and technical info like IP address and device type.

2. How We Use Your Data

To create accounts, provide support, process requests, ensure security, and comply with legal obligations.

3. How We Protect Data

We use encryption, firewalls, access controls, audits, backups, and international security standards to safeguard your data.

4. Sharing with Third Parties

We don’t share data unless required by law, consented by you, or needed for integrations/services. Contractors are bound by strict NDAs.

5. Your Rights

Depending on your location, you may access, modify, delete, or request portability of your data, and withdraw consent anytime.

6. Data Retention

We store your data as long as necessary to provide services or meet legal obligations. Old or unused data is anonymized or deleted.

7. Changes

We may update this Privacy Policy and notify users of significant changes. Continuing to use STOQ means you agree to the new version.

8. Contact Us

For questions, contact us at{" "} contact@stoq.ai .
